{{- /* Clawbot-only ~/.aws/config: per-profile regions for the caged agent. The
       placeholder profiles seeded in ~/.aws/credentials carry no region, and a
       named profile does NOT inherit region from [default], so `aws --profile
       develop …` fails with NoRegion unless a matching [profile develop] with a
       region exists. The profile names mirror the accounts, so — like the
       credentials file — the content lives in the private overlay, never the
       public repo.

       stat-guarded, so the public repo stands alone and a human box keeps its
       own aws-sso-managed ~/.aws/config untouched (its overlay carries no such
       file, so this symlink dangles); on a clawbot the overlay supplies the file
       and this symlink resolves. Same idiom as symlink_credentials.tmpl. */ -}}
{{- $src := joinPath .chezmoi.sourceDir ".." "private" "home" "aws" "config" -}}
{{- if stat $src }}{{ $src }}{{ end -}}
